  "remarks": "\nZhengHeng Group Co. Ltd (“ZhengHeng Group”) is an involved person under the Global Human Rights Sanctions Regulations 2020 is an involved person under the Global Human Rights Sanctions Regulations 2020 because it has facilitated or provided support for or obtained benefit from activity that violates the to be free from slavery, not to be held in servitude or required to perform forced or compulsory labour Specifically, individuals were held at Long Bay Development premises owned by ZhengHeng Group where they were forced to work as scammers \n",
